title: I'll Name This Podcast Later Episode 40
description: In Joe's absence, due to the "All Love Lost Tour", we brought in friends of the show; Lowkey, Scottie Beam, and Gia to discuss courting, condoms, nudes, etc. After 40 weeks of speaking about him, Ty Dolla Sign joins the podcast to discuss his album "Free TC" and him and Mari's friendship/fandom.
